{"tid":2239675,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本土banker邊緣化｜中資券商不願聘港人 投行港人佔比2年降約10百分點","createTime":"2020-10-12T06:34:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T06:58:22.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ded64de633669abaf985e7c6d6ce6b5c315436b7","tid":2239675,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:34:30.000Z","msg":"港股A股化，加上一連串社會事件，本土banker近年逐漸被邊緣化。外媒報道，投行職位中港人佔比由2年前40%，降約10個百份點，至約30%。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報道，香港本地人才正在迅速香港首選投資銀行家地位，取而代之的是中國大陸的競爭者，他們現於香港擔任大多數高級職位。而最近變化幅度，甚至震動了業內資深人士，他們歸咎去年逆權活動後，中資券商不願再僱用和晉升香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201012/ASYX6Q2QZ5AGNNCBB4BNJ72ASU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201012%2FASYX6Q2QZ5AGNNCBB4BNJ72ASU%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBX0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=3f489e3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201012%2FASYX6Q2QZ5AGNNCBB4BNJ72ASU%2F&h=e5cb49a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201012/ASYX6Q2QZ5AGNNCBB4BNJ72ASU/</a>"},{"pid":"e7ad7bd21eeb92f80e6968694bf89c36c7b6dffb","tid":2239675,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-10-11/hong-kong-bankers-are-losing-their-jobs-to-mainland-china-rivals\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-10-11%2Fhong-kong-bankers-are-losing-their-jobs-to-mainland-china-rivals&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBX0iZiuoirEQNng52NyFBY4%3D&h=1bc890bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-10-11/hong-kong-bankers-are-losing-their-jobs-to-mainland-china-rivals</a>"},{"pid":"2c23d9d375e7b67a5e9cd4b4b95cf571870d9aab","tid":2239675,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"投行都唔好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/n